A Malayalam film Thirakkatha (2008) was based on the relationship between Kamal and
Srividya in their early early years. It won National Award for the Best Feature Film in Malayalam.
In 1960, Kamal was awarded Rashtrapathi Award for his performance in Kalathur Kannamma.
Kamal has been awarded Kalaimamani award by the government of Tamil Nadu and also the
prestigious Padmashree award by the government of India.
In 2000, he wrote to the Filmfare commitee requesting not to award him further.
